column5: Hi everyone, I need to pick up a new battery for my finder before the weekend. I've been using a 12v 7a battery for years and they work great for the weight (kayak and rental boats).  Anyone know where I can pick them up in Toronto (quick google isn't helping).  This is what I'm looking for:    Thanks Sean
Radioworld?  Any of the sat shops on Matheson as well just west of Dixie.
Lebarons have them  Or  SAYAL Electronics 3791 unit 1-5 Victoria Park Ave Markham  SAYAL Electronics 7701 unit 1-3 Woodbine Ave Markham
Any electrical supply store, sail, BPS, Lebarons......they all have them. Usually around $25.  S.
Trailer breakaway battery at princess auto
